{"tid":667782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"出事喇！都話未贏冠軍前唔好摸獎盃啦","createTime":"2018-05-17T04:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T10:23:46.000Z","uid":54870,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d69cc107b0a155c3616ca81a9e1b2aef422362b4","tid":667782,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"馬賽喺歐霸盃決賽以0:3不敵馬德里體育會，賽後傳媒發現，原來馬賽隊長皮耶喺開波前，行出球員通道後用左手摸咗獎盃一下，犯咗足球禁忌，結果佢唔止喺上半場傷出，最後仲失埋個冠軍，搞到爆喊要對手基沙文錫佢面豬呵番呀！<br />\n<br />\n皮耶帶傷上陣，上半場中段已經因傷離場。賽後有傳媒提起，未贏冠軍摸獎盃係足球禁忌，當中最出名係2005年歐聯決賽，AC米蘭喺半場領先利物浦3:0嘅情況下，加度素返更衣室前多手摸獎盃，最後AC下半場被連追3球，互射12碼輸埋出事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20180517091452377-0517_00882_001&amp;whichpage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2Fnewe%2Findex.html%3FarticleId%3Dbkn-20180517091452377-0517_00882_001%26whichpage%3D1&d=28MNBqwg5GCie43WYRViMk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=44bc24ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20180517091452377-0517_00882_001&amp;whichpage=1</a>"},{"pid":"8f002e50f2c59c75351e113cd91167c795a6e0d7","tid":667782,"uid":37735,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T04:52:55.000Z","msg":"反正都輸<br />\n做全隊唯一一個摸過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a488eef9334d176c2a7e07d564c337d2d91a3476","tid":667782,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T04:57: